reviews.review_text: Great sounding! To the people who care about really good sounding recordings of GD shows. This is one.

After Midnight! I was at this show & wanted to correct the "notes" section.  Due to a long show (and maybe a late start), it was approaching midnight during Not Fade Away.  Allegedly, the Fire Marshal had the stage lights shut off to get the band to stop playing.  It didn't work though - they segued into Lovelight, playing in the dark! You know that pissed-off Hartford's security - my friends & I were totally pump!

Very good show, Jerry had soul this night! Sound is very good too!
